title: It Cosmetics Bye Bye Pores HD Silk Micro-Powder 1 ea
description: HD Silk Micro Finishing Anti-Aging Powder from It Cosmetics is infused with Collagen, Vitamin K and Pure Silk for the perfect poreless airbrushed finish.Say goodbye to visible Pores with the HD Silk Micro Finishing Powder from It Cosmetics. title: Benefit Cosmetics Feelin' Cheeky! Minis (Boxed)
description: Benefit Cosmetics Feelin' Cheeky! Minis is a selection of three of Benefit Cosmetics three bestselling cheek products. A little goes a long way. They are long lasting and provide a gorgeous subtle natural look. You get one 0.13oz each of the following: - Benetint Rose-tinted lip & cheek stain. Benetint is the award winning Lip & Cheek stain. It provides a beautiful sheer rose-colored tint that gives your lips & cheeks natural looking healthy glow that is smudge-proof, kiss-proof and water-proof. - Posietint Poppy-pink tinted lip & cheek stain. This kiss of see-through poppy-pink tint brightens cheeks & lips. - Highbeam luminescent complexion enhancer (shimmering pale pink). Use anywhere you want to highlight; cheek, brow and more

title: Urban Decay Eyeshadow Primer Potion Tube - Eden
description: What it is:A tawny matte eye shadow primer.  What it does:Packaged in a new squeeze tube with a precise needle nose, this triple-duty product also works as a highlighter or eye shadow. Perfect for more mature customers or those who want to avoid shimmer, this versatile shade instantly brightens the eyes and provides the ultimate prep for creaseless, more vibrant shadow and all-day wear. What else you need to know:  The squeeze tube version of this product is exclusive to Sephora for a limited time.
